OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772637083
OL,3,CBoy, 8, spends pocket money doing
OL,4,Crandom acts of kindness
OL,6,FAn eight-year-old boy who spends his
OL,7,Fpocket money on "random acts of
OL,8,Fkindness" says he wants to "show
OL,9,Fpeople that there is still kindness
OL,10,Fout there".
OL,12,FRowan Stapleton, who's from Salford,
OL,13,Fwalks round the streets of Salford and
OL,14,FManchester handing out chocolates and
OL,15,Fflowers to people to try and brighten
OL,16,Ftheir day.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
