PN,39402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772637083
OL,3,CBoy, 8, spends pocket money doing
OL,4,Crandom acts of kindness
OL,6,FRowan said: "I saw a Christmas advert
OL,7,Fof a dad building a go kart out of
OL,8,Fwood and it made me sad so I asked my
OL,9,Fmum if I could use my pocket money to
OL,10,Fmake people smile."
OL,12,FWhether it's after school or on a
OL,13,Fweekend, Rowan wants to go out and
OL,14,Fmake people smile. Now he wants to get
OL,15,Fhis teammates involved as well.
OL,17,F"Maybe one day after we have played
OL,18,Ffootball, I could just tell my
OL,19,Ffootball coach if we can go out with
OL,20,Fmy football team and help people."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772637083
OL,3,CBoy, 8, spends pocket money doing
OL,4,Crandom acts of kindness
OL,6,FDaryl Dylan, Rowan's football coach
OL,7,Fsaid: "I think kids would love it as
OL,8,Fwell. They don't understand what these
OL,9,Flittle things do for people. I think
OL,10,Fit's amazing if he gets his team
OL,11,Finvolved.
OL,13,F"He is a lovely child and has got a
OL,14,Fheart of gold. Always looking after
OL,15,Fpeople, he's always making sure that I
OL,16,Fam okay, that his friends are okay
OL,17,Ftoo. He is an amazing kid."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
