CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772637083
OL,3,CBoy, 8, spends pocket money doing
OL,4,Crandom acts of kindness
OL,6,FRowan added: "It makes me feel like
OL,7,Fi've had a nice day because I have
OL,8,Fhelped someone out for the day and I
OL,9,Fhave at least done something to help
OL,10,Fsomeone. it can show people that there
OL,11,Fis still kindness out there."
OL,13,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,14,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,15,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,16,Four region.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
